                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12642883" author="jorgenlo" created="Mon, 27 Oct 2008 10:00:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch removes the NPE by setting RawStoreFactory in LogFactory before starting slave replication mode. The patch removes the only currently known problem related to replication of encrypted databases.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A separate jira has been created for testing replication of encrypted databases, so this patch does not include any test cases.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12642904" author="knutanders" created="Mon, 27 Oct 2008 12:19:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks correct to me. I&apos;ve performed some manual tests and I haven&apos;t been able to break anything. +1 to commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12643175" author="jorgenlo" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2008 10:26:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reviewing the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;derby-3890-1.diff committed with revision 708510.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12643179" author="jorgenlo" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2008 10:40:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changing to type &quot;improvement&quot; since this fix enables replication of encrypted databases.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12874541" author="kristwaa" created="Wed, 2 Jun 2010 12:11:58 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
